OL,3,CWoman 'chased' and sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cwhile out running
OL,6,FA woman who was out on a run was
OL,7,Fchased and then sexually assaulted by
OL,8,Fa man in Cheltenham.
OL,10,FIt happened on Sunday 11 February just
OL,11,Fbefore 8.30am on the Honeybourne Line,
OL,12,Fclose to the Queen's Road end.
OL,14,FThe Honeybourne Line is a track that
OL,15,Fruns from Cheltenham railway station
OL,16,Fand Queens Road to Tommy Taylors Lane,
OL,17,FPittville Park, and Wymans Brook.
