OL,3,CWoman 'chased' and sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cwhile out running
OL,6,FA woman in her 30s spotted a man who
OL,7,F"appeared to be talking to himself and
OL,8,Fwalking around in circles",
OL,9,FGloucestershire Police said.
OL,11,FAs she passed him, he began to run
OL,12,Fafter her before "touching her bottom".
OL,14,FShe ran faster and the man then walked
OL,15,Foff in the opposite direction, towards
OL,16,Fthe town centre.
OL,18,FThe man was described as being white,
OL,19,Faged in his 40s, about 5ft 7in in
OL,20,Fheight, and of a slim build.
