OL,3,CWoman 'chased' and sexually assaulted
OL,4,Cwhile out running
OL,6,FHe had a reddish-blonde bushy beard
OL,7,Fand was wearing a pale blue
OL,8,Fneckerchief, a dirty grey Beanie hat,
OL,9,Fa round-necked jumper, and jeans worn
OL,10,Flow, revealing boxer shorts beneath.
OL,11,FHe was also wearing a backpack.
OL,13,FPolice say they would like to speak to
OL,14,Fanyone who may have seen a person
OL,15,Facting suspiciously in the area at
OL,16,Faround that time, or who has any other
OL,17,Finformation which may be relevant.
OL,19,FAnybody who can assist is asked to
OL,20,Fcontact Gloucestershire Constabulary ,
OL,21,Fquoting incident 104 of 11 February.
